<section>
	<section class="hbox stretch wizard">
		<aside> 
			<section class="vbox">
				<header class="header bg-white b-b clearfix">
				  <div class="row">
				  	<div class="col-sm-4">
				  		<%= link_to wizard_homepage_gallery_path, class: "btn btn-default" do %>
				    	 	Back
				    	<% end %>
				  	</div>
				    <div class="col-sm-4">
				  		50% complete
				    	<div class="progress progress-xs" style="margin:0"> 
								<div class="progress-bar bg-info" data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="50%" style="width: 50%">
				    		</div> 
				    	</div>
				    </div>
				    <div class="col-sm-4 text-right">
				    	<%= link_to dashboard_path, class: "btn btn-danger" do %>
				    	 	<span style="font-weight:700;">Exit Wizard</span>
				    	<% end %>
				    </div>
				  </div>
				</header>
				<section class="scrollable wrapper finished">
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="add-page">
			        <div class="row">
			          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
			          	<div class="top-info center">
							      <h1>Almost finished!</h1>
							      <div class="row">
							      	<div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
									      <p class="m-t-lg">Now we need to add pages, availabilities, and contacts to your website. But, we're going to have to 
									      	exit the wizard in order to complete these final steps. Your dashboard will have the appropriate links to
									        complete these tasks. But, here are a few steps to help you get started.</p>
								      </div>
								    </div>
							    </div>
			        		<section class="steps">
			        			<h2>Step 1: Add Pages</h2>
			        			<p>You can add and manage your pages in the "Pages" section of your dashboard. You can upload an optional image for each of 
			        				 your pages. Pages only accept one image per page. <%= link_to "Add new page", new_page_path %></p>
			        			<%= image_tag('/assets/addpage.jpg', class: "img-responsive img-thumbnail") %>
			        		</section>
			        		<section class="steps">
			        			<h2>Step 2: Add Availabilities</h2>
			        			<p>You can add and manage your availability listings in the "Availabilities" section of your dashboard. Unlike pages, you may upload mulitple images to showcase your space. <%= link_to "Add new listing", new_availability_path %></p>
			        			<%= image_tag('/assets/addlisting.jpg', class: "img-responsive img-thumbnail") %>
			        		</section>
			        		<section class="steps">
			        			<h2>Step 3: Add Contacts</h2>
			        			<p>You can add your colleages contacts that are associated with this property. <%= link_to "Add new contacts", new_contact_path %></p>
			        			<%= image_tag('/assets/contacts.jpg', class: "img-responsive img-thumbnail") %>
			        		</section>
			          </div>
			        </div>
			      </div>
		      </div>
				</section>
			</section>
		</aside>
	</section>
	
</section>



























